<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Share Ideas - Bonded</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: whitesmoke;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.8;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        footer {
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
         
        }

        .content-container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .text {
            max-width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
        }

            .text h1 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #333;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .text h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                margin-top: 20px;
                color: #444;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

            .text p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .text ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
            }

                .text ul li {
                    font-size: 1.1rem;
                    margin-bottom: 10px;
                    padding-left: 20px;
                    position: relative;
                }

                    .text ul li:before {
                        content: "✔";
                        color: crimson;
                        position: absolute;
                        left: 0;
                    }

        .image-container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
        }

            .image-container img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="text">
            <h1>Share Ideas</h1>
            <p>
                Express your thoughts and inspirations on Bonded. Create a space to share knowledge, creativity, and insights with a global community. Whether you're exploring new ideas, exchanging advice, or simply brainstorming, Bonded provides the perfect platform to engage with others and fuel your creativity.
            </p>
            <h2>What You Can Share</h2>
            <p>
                Bonded is designed for anyone looking to share their experiences, thoughts, and projects. Here's how you can use our platform:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Creative Ideas:</strong> Share your artistic, scientific, or innovative ideas with others and get feedback from a like-minded community.</li>
                <li><strong>Expert Advice:</strong> Provide valuable insights in your field of expertise, or ask for advice from professionals and peers.</li>
                <li><strong>Collaborative Projects:</strong> Start collaborative projects with other users and bring your ideas to life together.</li>
                <li><strong>Learning Resources:</strong> Share useful resources, guides, or tutorials to help others grow their knowledge and skills.</li>
                <li><strong>Inspiration:</strong> Inspire others with your journey, challenges, and successes, helping to motivate a worldwide audience.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Join the Community</h2>
            <p>
                Bonded is a space where creative minds unite. By sharing your ideas, you'll not only inspire others but also gain inspiration in return. Together, we can build a powerful community of innovative thinkers and changemakers.
            </p>
            <p>
                Start sharing today and see how your ideas can make a global impact!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image below the content, occupying full width -->
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="~/images/kindel2.jpg" alt="Share Ideas">
    </div>
